name: Skriptbridge
tagline: A Skript add-on which hooks a bunch of plugins.
body:
### Welcome to SkriptBridge's Github Page
Skript bridge is an awesome add-on for Skript that adds support for many other plugins. If you want to check out the code or read the documentation, you've came to the right place.
